WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:45.040
I wonder how Su Ning is doing.

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:47.000
I need to familiarize myself with the situation quickly

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.800
and find her as soon as possible.

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:50.080
Lord Prefect.

00:00:50.560 --> 00:00:51.520
To be honest,

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:53.120
after this imprisonment,

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.520
I can't remember many things from the past.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:57.560
Do you know the full story of my case?

00:00:57.880 --> 00:00:59.800
When I was locked up on death row,

00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:01.280
your case was tried by that evil Taoist.

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:03.120
I reviewed the case file again yesterday

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:04.800
and found many suspicious points.

00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:05.480
The file says

00:01:05.480 --> 00:01:07.400
that because you were unhappy your father left all the property

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:09.120
to your illegitimate cousin,

00:01:09.120 --> 00:01:10.680
you bore a grudge

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.080
and poisoned him to frame someone else.

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.400
The authorities arrested you

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:15.160
on the spot in Luoxian Town.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.080
Luoxian Town.

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:18.560
But

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:20.840
after spending these past few days with you,

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:21.680
I found

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:22.920
that you are loyal,

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:24.240
quick-witted and courageous.

00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:26.320
There must be a reason behind it.

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.810
It's probably just another drama of schemes,

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:30.920
deception,

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:32.780
and fighting over family assets.

00:01:33.479 --> 00:01:36.120
There is nothing new under the sun.

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:37.680
Luoxian Town.

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:38.800
The Lin family.

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.080
It seems...

00:01:40.080 --> 00:01:41.740
It is necessary to make a trip.

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.160
Governor.

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:47.200
This is the chief of Tianji Pavilion,

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:48.280
Su Wuhui.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:49.440
You are Lin Mo.

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:51.960
Nice to meet you.

00:01:51.960 --> 00:01:53.680
You have done a great deed by subduing the great demon Yuantong.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:56.880
The Empress ordered me to take you to the palace to see her.

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:58.120
Ouch, ouch, ouch.

00:01:59.080 --> 00:02:01.080
Don't tell me we have to ride horses.

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:04.840
My dear niece.

00:02:05.960 --> 00:02:08.320
I have waited for this day for too long.

00:02:08.320 --> 00:02:09.400
Your Majesty.

00:02:09.400 --> 00:02:13.200
You and my nephew have no blood relation at all.

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:15.480
There's no need to worry.

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:17.920
Just endure it for one night and it will be over.

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:21.360
I'll just stay here and watch your performance.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:28.680
You two old fogeys,

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:30.000
who gave you the nerve

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:32.400
to collude with the Beijing monster tribe,

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:33.860
transform into monsters,

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:36.360
and even dare to humiliate the emperor?

00:02:36.880 --> 00:02:38.280
Humiliate the emperor?

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:39.880
The current Daqian

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.079
cannot defeat the powerful Beijing outside,

00:02:42.079 --> 00:02:44.800
and is controlled by the powerful minister Lin Youtang inside.

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:46.079
You, as an emperor,

00:02:46.079 --> 00:02:48.040
are just like a puppet.

00:02:48.320 --> 00:02:49.360
Qian'er,

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:50.640
hurry up.

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:52.440
Our time is limited.

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:53.520
After you consummate,

00:02:53.520 --> 00:02:55.480
you still need to make her take the monster seed

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:57.480
so we can completely control her.

00:02:57.720 --> 00:02:59.440
Understood, Aunt.

00:03:12.320 --> 00:03:13.800
If a tiger doesn't show its might,

00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:15.400
you think I'm a sick cat?

00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:18.530
The monster body is indeed strong.

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:27.600
It can't even die from this.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:28.760
You guys...

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:30.840
to achieve immortality,

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.040
you even gave up being human.

00:03:32.040 --> 00:03:35.040
A monster body can easily live for hundreds of years.

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:37.240
It's very promising.

00:03:37.640 --> 00:03:38.800
Stop struggling,

00:03:39.079 --> 00:03:40.040
Niece Ningxue.

00:03:40.280 --> 00:03:42.840
My Xue family supported your father in founding the state.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.040
It's not too much for me, Xue Qian, to ask for some interest now,

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:46.040
is it?

00:03:46.320 --> 00:03:47.600
Think of something quickly, Su Ning.

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:49.600
I'd rather die than let him succeed.

00:03:49.600 --> 00:03:50.400
What should I do?

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:51.320
Think quickly.

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:54.160
What other trump cards do I have in this book?

00:03:54.160 --> 00:03:55.280
I am now Su Ningxue,

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.079
not Su Ning.

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.920
I am the emperor of Daqian.

00:03:59.120 --> 00:03:59.920
Right.

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:05.560
That's right.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:06.600
Niece Ningxue,

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:08.800
give up the resistance.

00:04:12.880 --> 00:04:13.880
Sword!

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:19.860
The late Emperor's Shanhe Sword.

00:04:21.880 --> 00:04:24.800
You actually got the Shanhe Sword's approval.

00:04:25.400 --> 00:04:28.160
Qian'er.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:32.400
You witch!

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:33.720
Villains always talk too much.

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.650
How can you wield the Shanhe Sword?

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:36.680
Witch?

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:38.760
Witch?

00:04:39.200 --> 00:04:40.840
Are you kidding me?

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.000
You have a tongue several meters long,

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:44.480
and you call me a witch?

00:04:46.280 --> 00:04:48.640
Die!

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:02.540
What are you doing?

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:06.400
What are you doing?

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:08.200
I rode all the way here.

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:09.520
You grabbed me all the way.

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:10.760
What do you think I'm doing?

00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:11.360
I...

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:12.560
I told you,

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:14.200
I don't know how to ride a horse.

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:14.920
Besides holding on tight,

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:16.050
what else could I do?

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:17.800
Commander Su!

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:18.320
Bad news!

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:19.480
His Majesty went to Cihou Palace.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:20.440
It's been an hour,

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:21.970
and he hasn't returned yet.

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.600
He just went to ask questions.

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.530
Why would he be delayed for so long?

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:30.480
How is your Emperor's relationship with the Grand Empress Dowager?

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.410
What do you mean?

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:34.120
Think about it.

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:36.680
If they don't have a good relationship,

00:05:36.680 --> 00:05:39.210
and his most trusted guards aren't around...

00:05:41.080 --> 00:05:41.800
Oh no!

00:05:42.159 --> 00:05:43.560
His Majesty is in danger!

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:45.840
Liu Wancai.

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:46.840
His Majesty is in trouble.

00:05:46.840 --> 00:05:49.440
Come to Cihou Palace for support immediately!

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:54.159
If I don't make a contribution now

00:05:54.159 --> 00:05:54.800
and leave a good impression,

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.000
what am I waiting for?

00:05:57.840 --> 00:05:58.500
Wait for me!

00:05:58.560 --> 00:05:59.400
I can help you!

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:01.130
I can also protect His Majesty!

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:07.480
Oh no.

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.920
Hurry back to the palace and save His Majesty.

00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:09.840
Hyah.

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:40.240
Stop them.

00:06:40.320 --> 00:06:40.880
Charge.

00:06:40.960 --> 00:06:41.800
Yes.

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:48.360
Hold them off.

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:49.760
I'll go save His Majesty.

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.320
Rescuing the Emperor alone

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:04.080
is a great merit.

00:07:04.080 --> 00:07:05.000
Tonight,

00:07:05.080 --> 00:07:06.040
I will make you...

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.000
Your Majesty.

00:07:10.080 --> 00:07:12.200
I have come to save you.

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:17.160
Ling Mo.

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:18.800
Wife.

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:20.800
You...

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.330
What class are you playing?

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:27.040
Watch out!

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:32.800
Are you okay?

00:07:35.200 --> 00:07:36.200
What is this?

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:54.920
Monster eliminated.

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:56.440
Acquired new bonus skill:

00:07:56.440 --> 00:07:57.600
Clear Conscience.

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.560
Cooldown time:

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.440
Two hours.

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.840
I am late to rescue you.

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:06.720
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:07.400
Your...

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.290
You are the Emperor?

00:08:09.640 --> 00:08:10.080
I...

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:11.970
How dare you!

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.960
A commoner must not disrespect Your Majesty. I...

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:14.400
I...

00:08:15.880 --> 00:08:16.680
I'm sorry.

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:20.720
This damn guy.

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:22.520
I knew he wouldn't die so easily.

00:08:22.640 --> 00:08:24.120
A weed never dies.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:25.760
Let's protect him first.

00:08:26.520 --> 00:08:27.280
Liu Wancai.

00:08:27.760 --> 00:08:28.440
Yes.

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.840
Tie this lecher up,

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:32.760
and send him

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:35.559
to my bedchamber.

00:08:35.799 --> 00:08:36.600
Yes.

00:08:40.039 --> 00:08:40.840
Your Majesty,

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:42.240
I am here to save you.

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:44.039
I am innocent, Your Ma...

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:48.340
I'll settle the score with you later.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:57.840
This body under twenty is just amazing.

00:08:58.280 --> 00:09:00.120
Ling Mo has gotten younger too.

00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:01.840
And quite handsome.

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:07.520
Liu Wancai.

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:10.440
I need an explanation.

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:11.960
Your Majesty.

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:13.000
I was careless

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:14.660
and received a forged decree.

00:09:14.840 --> 00:09:16.320
After I was far from the palace

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:17.920
and received Commander Su's plea for help,

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:19.320
I realized something was wrong

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:20.980
and rushed back immediately.

00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:22.440
In the book, Liu Wancai

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:24.640
is my most loyal guard.

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:26.740
I should treat him sincerely.

00:09:27.560 --> 00:09:28.440
Forget it.

00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:29.880
Be careful next time.

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:31.680
I only have one life.

00:09:31.880 --> 00:09:33.280
Even ten thousand deaths

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:35.640
wouldn't be enough to repay Your Majesty's grace.

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:37.900
I will protect Your Majesty with my life.

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:40.640
Your Majesty.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:43.080
How should we deal with these people?

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:44.200
Execute the rest.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:45.920
Put him

00:09:45.920 --> 00:09:47.840
in prison and interrogate him slowly.

00:09:47.840 --> 00:09:48.900
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:50.720
The world in this book is extremely dangerous.

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:51.920
I must survive first.

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.560
I am no longer Su Ning.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.120
I am Empress Su Ningxue.

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:57.720
What happened in the Empress Dowager's Palace tonight

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:58.780
must not be leaked.

00:09:58.960 --> 00:09:59.880
Violators will have

00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:01.440
their entire families executed.

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.240
Yes.

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:04.120
Take my tiger tally

00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:05.240
to the Kyoto Garrison Camp

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:06.520
and pass on my oral decree.

00:10:06.520 --> 00:10:08.320
Xue Qian, son of Duke Xue,

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:09.560
colluded with the Beijing demons,

00:10:09.560 --> 00:10:10.800
deceived the Grand Empress Dowager,

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:12.120
and intended to murder me.

00:10:12.120 --> 00:10:13.320
His crimes are heinous.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:15.280
Execute the three generations of the Xue family.

00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:17.320
Take the commanders and confiscate their property.

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:18.520
Before sunrise,

00:10:18.680 --> 00:10:20.080
everything that moves

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:20.960
and breathes in the Xue family,

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:22.960
including their insects and mice,

00:10:23.520 --> 00:10:24.780
must not be left alive.

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:26.780
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:10:33.760 --> 00:10:35.320
I was so cool just now.

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:38.980
Watching all those historical idol dramas wasn't in vain.

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.360
What is it, my son?

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:50.140
The Xue family is gone.

00:10:50.680 --> 00:10:53.410
Imperial Sister didn't leave a single survivor.

00:10:54.560 --> 00:10:55.680
I know.

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:58.200
Relying on their founding fathers,

00:10:58.560 --> 00:11:00.320
they really went too far.

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:02.000
My son,

00:11:02.200 --> 00:11:03.360
you may go.

00:11:03.760 --> 00:11:04.440
Yes.

00:11:08.160 --> 00:11:09.320
Empress,

00:11:09.640 --> 00:11:11.360
the gift I have for you,

00:11:11.760 --> 00:11:13.600
are you ready to receive it?

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:21.960
Good job.

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:23.920
Finally, a weight is off my mind.

00:11:40.400 --> 00:11:41.800
Su Ning,

00:11:42.280 --> 00:11:43.160
is that you?

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:45.770
Odd changes, even doesn't.

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:48.680
Royal Jade Liquor.

00:11:48.680 --> 00:11:49.440
How dare you!

00:11:50.760 --> 00:11:51.560
Spouting nonsense

00:11:51.560 --> 00:11:53.160
and disturbing Her Majesty.

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:54.720
What do you mean?

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:57.480
You are so insolent in front of me.

00:11:58.080 --> 00:11:59.760
As a subject of Daqian,

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:01.840
you show no respect for your sovereign.

00:12:01.840 --> 00:12:03.100
Who gave you the nerve?

00:12:03.520 --> 00:12:04.880
Did I get the wrong person?

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:06.240
She is not my wife.

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:10.050
It seems you are still defiant.

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:12.160
Slap his face.

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:14.480
No, no, no.

00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:16.160
I submit.

00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:17.400
I submit, okay?

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:21.300
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:24.680
Looking at you,

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:26.320
you are quite attractive.

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:29.000
Huaiyang salt merchant Lin Mo,

00:12:29.560 --> 00:12:31.320
not only did you save the Governor of Huaiyang

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.650
and subdue the monster,

00:12:32.760 --> 00:12:35.220
but you also did a great service by saving me.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.080
You are quite capable.

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:39.480
Let me think.

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:41.960
What should I reward you with?

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:44.280
Or,

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:46.920
give you an official position.

00:12:49.960 --> 00:12:51.040
Here comes the chance.

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:52.280
Let me show you

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:54.010
the terror of a future STEM guy.

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:56.840
I am good at inventing.

00:12:56.840 --> 00:12:58.640
I can join the Ministry of Works.

00:12:58.800 --> 00:12:59.840
Ah.

00:12:59.840 --> 00:13:00.960
You want to enter the palace?

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:02.400
I am very pleased.

00:13:09.280 --> 00:13:10.480
Why not

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:12.960
become the Chief Eunuch

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:16.400
and stay by my side forever?

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:19.040
Eu...

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:19.880
Eunuch?

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:21.560
No, sister.

00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:23.600
I want to join the Ministry of Works,

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:25.000
not enter the palace.

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:27.120
Your Majesty.

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:28.080
I was presumptuous.

00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:28.920
I apologize.

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:30.880
I was wrong.

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:31.560
Put down the sword.

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:32.880
Can we talk nicely?

00:13:33.400 --> 00:13:34.160
Don't come closer.

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:34.720
If you come any closer,

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:35.520
I will scream.

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:38.480
Help!

00:13:41.080 --> 00:13:42.280
That was satisfying.

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:43.490
I've had enough fun.

00:13:43.640 --> 00:13:44.840
You may all step down.

00:13:58.760 --> 00:14:00.080
How have you been,

00:14:01.280 --> 00:14:02.280
my ex-husband?

00:14:03.080 --> 00:14:03.840
Ah!

00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:16.400
Got the demon core.

00:14:16.400 --> 00:14:18.400
That was effortless.

00:14:19.160 --> 00:14:20.640
A worthwhile trip.

00:14:31.280 --> 00:14:32.280
Lin Mo.

00:14:33.240 --> 00:14:35.240
Fine.

00:14:35.920 --> 00:14:37.520
We have plenty of time ahead.

00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:47.240
We both transmigrated into a book.

00:14:47.240 --> 00:14:49.240
Why are you the ceiling of humanity,

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:51.680
while I start with getting my head chopped off?

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:53.810
Who told you to act inhumanely before?

00:14:53.920 --> 00:14:55.360
This is karma.

00:14:56.080 --> 00:14:56.640
Fine.

00:14:56.880 --> 00:14:58.680
I worried about you for nothing.

00:14:58.680 --> 00:15:00.040
If you want to be the emperor,

00:15:00.040 --> 00:15:01.360
just stay here and be it.

00:15:01.360 --> 00:15:02.960
I need to go to the Lin family.

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:04.360
Once the spring dries up,

00:15:04.760 --> 00:15:05.560
my life

00:15:05.840 --> 00:15:07.080
will come to an end.

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:10.800
What...

00:15:10.800 --> 00:15:12.320
What kind of crappy setting is this?

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:13.920
What does this spring have to do with you?

00:15:13.920 --> 00:15:15.520
This is the Fengming Spring.

00:15:15.560 --> 00:15:17.620
It symbolizes the destiny of Daqian.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:19.600
Once the spring dries up,

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:21.420
Daqian will be destroyed.

00:15:22.160 --> 00:15:22.960
Uncle.

00:15:23.680 --> 00:15:25.140
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:29.020
Is there any way to avoid this?

00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:30.320
Eliminate the demons

00:15:31.080 --> 00:15:32.610
and revitalize the nation.

00:15:32.880 --> 00:15:35.480
There is a place sealing an ancient great demon

00:15:35.720 --> 00:15:36.960
named Chamozu.

00:15:37.920 --> 00:15:40.400
The seal has loosened now.

00:15:40.760 --> 00:15:42.400
With the dragon aura, Your Majesty

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:44.480
is the only one who can strengthen the seal

00:15:44.480 --> 00:15:46.720
and not fear Chamozu's demonic magic.

00:15:47.240 --> 00:15:48.240
So I...

00:15:48.800 --> 00:15:49.760
must I

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:51.400
go there in person?

00:15:51.760 --> 00:15:54.360
Only Your Majesty can seal the great demon.

00:15:54.680 --> 00:15:56.000
But the sealed place

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:57.640
is now heavily infested with demons.

00:15:57.640 --> 00:15:59.360
The journey is full of dangers.

00:15:59.360 --> 00:16:00.760
Your Majesty, please

00:16:00.760 --> 00:16:02.200
consider it carefully.

00:16:02.840 --> 00:16:03.720
Uncle,

00:16:03.960 --> 00:16:05.420
I also want to find someone

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:06.600
named Han Qingyun.

00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:09.200
He is crucial to me.

00:16:20.080 --> 00:16:22.040
It's truly the will of Heaven, Your Majesty.

00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:24.840
The person you are looking for and the sealed place

00:16:24.840 --> 00:16:26.440
are both in his hometown,

00:16:27.880 --> 00:16:29.480
Luoxian Town.

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:39.960
Location: Luoxian Town.

00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:41.080
Monster: Unknown.

00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:42.160
Weakness: Unknown.

00:16:42.160 --> 00:16:42.760
Mission:

00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:44.960
Eliminate the monsters and subdue the Child of Destiny.

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:47.020
If you don't know, just don't show it.

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:48.900
Giving a quest hint would be fine.

00:16:50.440 --> 00:16:52.360
This looks quite normal.

00:16:52.520 --> 00:16:54.240
Uncle said it's a heavily monster-infested area.

00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:55.720
He wouldn't be fooling me, right?

00:16:55.720 --> 00:16:56.360
Miss,

00:16:56.600 --> 00:16:57.660
don't be careless.

00:16:57.760 --> 00:16:58.960
There is a rule here.

00:16:59.280 --> 00:17:00.720
Unless the bell rings,

00:17:00.840 --> 00:17:02.570
magical spells cannot be used.

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:04.480
Yes.

00:17:05.079 --> 00:17:06.440
The spells are sealed.

00:17:06.880 --> 00:17:08.680
I wonder if my skills can still be used.

00:17:08.680 --> 00:17:10.520
Besides the spells being sealed,

00:17:10.520 --> 00:17:11.880
are there any other taboos?

00:17:11.880 --> 00:17:12.319
Yes.

00:17:12.800 --> 00:17:14.599
But the writing has been erased.

00:17:14.680 --> 00:17:16.160
The people sent by Tianji Pavilion

00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:17.720
must have found some clues.

00:17:17.720 --> 00:17:18.520
But...

00:17:19.040 --> 00:17:19.880
But what?

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:22.280
It's just that before the message could be sent in,

00:17:22.280 --> 00:17:23.740
they were already killed.

00:17:24.640 --> 00:17:25.720
Without magical spells,

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:26.760
can you still fight?

00:17:26.760 --> 00:17:27.480
Yes.

00:17:27.800 --> 00:17:28.800
That's fine.

00:17:30.920 --> 00:17:31.800
Young Master.

00:17:33.160 --> 00:17:34.620
Young Master, is that you?

00:17:35.080 --> 00:17:35.640
No.

00:17:35.880 --> 00:17:36.960
Who are you, Miss?

00:17:37.160 --> 00:17:37.600
Miss.

00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:38.880
Do we know each other?

00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:39.880
Young Master.

00:17:39.880 --> 00:17:41.120
I've finally found you.

